//@10401    = ~Robe of Enfusing~
@10402    = ~Since the age of Netheril, wizards have learned to bestow a wide variety of magical properties upon the everyday objects that surround them. A favorite item of such enchantment is the common robe. It is lightweight, affordable, and holds its enchantment well, thereby making it ideal equipment for a wizard.

