@10571    = ~Plate of the Pit Fiend~
@10572    = ~No one is certain where the Plate of the Pit Fiend came from, or how it was created. Its spiky red scaled plates radiate a fiery red glow at all times, convincing those who look upon it that the plate mail is certainly otherworldly. 

