@10805    = ~Lolth's Sting +2~
@10806    = ~Blades such as this are often gifts to capable assassins in the service of Lolth. The entire weapon is as black as pitch and reflects no light; its grip is textured with a delicate web pattern while hundreds of tiny spiders are engraved along the two-foot blade. The short sword's dark magic not only protects the wielder from the effects of magical webs, but can entangle a target with webs of its own as well.

