Attack Bonus:  +2
Damage Type:  None
Special:
  Strength, proficiency, and other damage bonuses add to the healing of this weapon
  Brilliant Energy: Ignores target's armor and shield bonuses
Weight: 4 lb.
Feat Requirement:  Martial Weapon, Large Sword
Type:  One-handed~
