Attack Bonus:  +2
Enchantment:  +2
Damage Type:  Slashing
Special 
  Bane: +3 Attack Bonus vs Humans and +2d6+3 Damage Bonus vs Humans
Weight:  12 lb.
Feat Requirement:  Martial Weapon, Great Sword
Type:  Two-handed~
