Attack Bonus:  +5
Enchantment:  +5
Damage Type:  Bludgeoning
Special:
  Whenever the wielder takes damage, they have a 50% chance to gain +24 Strength for 2 rounds.
Weight: 5 lb.
Required Feat:  Martial Weapon, Flail
Type:  One-handed~
