@11602    = ~The Dire-Hammer Valorfoe is a frightful weapon, one forged to break an enemy's spirit as well as their armor and bones. It is ancient, its artisan's name long-lost even to the vast historical records of the gray dwarves. Covered in runes of cruel power, The Dire-Hammer Valorfoe bears a single inscription in the tongue of ancient dwarves, now used only by the duergar:

